query:
INSERT INTO vulnerabilities (name, severity , cve, cvss_score)
            VALUES ( ?, ?, ?, ? )
            ON CONFLICT (cve) DO UPDATE
            SET
                name = name,
                severity = severity,
                cvss_score = cvss_score
            RETURNING
                id,
                name,
                severity as "severity: _",
                cve,
                cvss_score
